Centos: [Doc avaialble on docker doc]
------- 
1) Install docker engine on VM or make it part of VM images using packer.
Sudo rpm -qa | grep -i docker -> Check docker installation
Systemctl status docker
Sudo systemctl start docker
Sudo systemctl enable docker
systemctl reload docker
Systemctl  status docker


tail -30 /var/log/messages


Ubuntu: [Document present in docker hub]
------
sudo cat /etc/lsb-release
sudo dpkg -l | grep -i docker -> Verify using native commands
Systemctl  status docker



- Install docker desktop